        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Strike</p>\n<hr />\n<p>A dwarven daisy is a string of dozens of firecrackers that create tiny, loud explosions. The string ends with a short, wrapped fuse. Pulling off the wrapping in a quick motion lights the fuse and is done as part of the action to Strike. A dwarven daisy deals the listed fire damage and splash damage. A dwarven daisy also has a chance to dazzle its target. A creature struck by a dwarven daisy must succeed at a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:18|name:Moderate Dwarven Daisy|showDC:all] save or become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Dazzled] for 1 round.</p>\n<p>The firework deals 2d6 fire damage and 2 fire splash damage. The DC is 18.</p>"
